.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-GRAPH-DEGREE-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-graph-degree-stats \- FEAT-2144 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-graph-degree-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2144).
.PP
Reports statistics on node connectivity in the local graph view, including
total node count, nodes with addresses, and nodes with aliases.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
